      <title>印度建立了世界上最长的液化石油气管道，以削减成本，不幸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/india-builds-world-s-longest-lpg-pipeline-to-cut-costs-mishaps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度经营的炼油厂将在6月之前完全委托全球最长的液化石油气管，这是一项关键开发项目，该开发项目将大幅降低燃油运输成本，并有助于预防致命的道路事故。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/india-builds-world-s-longest-lpg-pipeline-to-cut-costs-mishaps</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 05:23:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
